commit.message:
NamedTupleRow Fix and Settable Lowercase

Reasons for Change:
* NamedTupleRow and MutableNamedCursorRow do not work since `cursor._ColBufferList` is not instantiated at the time the `row_type_callable` is set up.
* `lowercase` is hardcoded, but developers will want a simple way of changing that without changing pypyodbc source

Description of Changes:
* Use `cursor.description` to instantiate the NamedTupleRow and MutableNamedTupleRow
* Make `lowercase` an optional kwarg for `Cursor` and `Connection.cursor`

NamedTupleRow Fix and Settable Lowercase

Reasons for Change:
* NamedTupleRow and MutableNamedCursorRow do not work since `cursor._ColBufferList` is not instantiated at the time the `row_type_callable` is set up.
* `lowercase` is hardcoded, but developers will want a simple way of changing that without changing pypyodbc source

Description of Changes:
* Use `cursor.description` to instantiate the NamedTupleRow and MutableNamedTupleRow
* Make `lowercase` an optional kwarg for `Cursor` and `Connection.cursor`
